    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798034084640.3470167256210709\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 61px; top: 65px; width: 676px; height: 431px; z-index: 17;\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 92, 92);\"><strong><em>dnf install git</em></strong></span></p><p></p><p>git --version (lista a vesrao que ta instalada )</p><p></p><p>definir nome do usuário</p><p>git config --global <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a> \"Radames Langner\"</p><p></p><p>mostra nome do usuário \"<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name\".</a></p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a></p><p><br></p><p>definir e-mail</p><p>git config --global <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.email\">user.email</a> \"<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:radahmes@gmail.com\">radahmes@gmail.com</a>\"</p><p></p><p>mostra o e-mail do usuário \"user.email\".</p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.email</a></p><p><br></p><p>define editor</p><p>git config --global core-editor vscode</p><p>git config <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\">user.name</a></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>show list</p><p><br></p><p>git config --list</p></div>",
    "<div class=\"metadata-header\" style=\"display:none;\">informatica|Git-Github|comandos|configuracoes</div><div class=\"canvas-box\" data-id=\"box-17798037426500.07187349609606275\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 63px; top: 67px; width: 620px; height: auto; z-index: 15;\"><p>show list</p><p></p><p>git config --list</p><p></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"http://user.name\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">user.name</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">=Radames Langner </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" href=\"mailto:user.email=radahmes@gmail.com\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\">user.email=radahmes@gmail.com</span></a><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: monospace;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\"><br></span>Criar repositorio (mkdir projeto)</p><p><br>Cria a pasta que deseja cirar pelo sistema ou pelo prompt ou terminal</p><p>Dentro da pasta que criada e que se deseja iniciar , com o comando :</p><p><br>git init - inicia a pasta, gera arquivo .git</p><p><br></p></div>"
